Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.81,0:00:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.14,0:00:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a pretty good swimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:01:01.78,Mushisode Title,,0,0,0,eptitle,{\fad(2000,0)\an9\bord0\blur0.6\p1\c&H6C927B&\pos(1290,66)\fscx600\fscy90}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100
Dialogue: 2,0:00:55.86,0:01:01.78,Mushisode Title,,0,0,0,eptitle,{\fad(2000,0)\an6\blur0.6\pos(980,108)}Azure Waters
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.41,0:01:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, better get moving.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.48,0:01:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.86,0:01:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the smoke get to you?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.46,0:01:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His skin is unusually cold...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.43,0:01:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}even for someone who's been swimming.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.24,0:01:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.29,0:01:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.51,0:01:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.13,0:01:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. What happened to him?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.01,0:01:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I think it was my fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.25,0:01:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have breathed in my cigarette smoke.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.66,0:02:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.82,0:02:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You certainly caught a lot again today, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.87,0:02:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's get ourselves home.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.59,0:02:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.05,0:02:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there something else?{Timing: Generous lead-out. :)}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.84,0:02:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I saw just now, \Nthat boy is quite the swimmer.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.79,0:02:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But does he happen to have \Ndifficulty with running?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.01,0:02:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if he does?{Interesting article: http://languagelog.ldc.upenn.edu/nll/?p=3483}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.35,0:02:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And is he always very thirsty, \Nperhaps even unusually so?{diabetes.}
Dialogue: 2,0:02:33.63,0:02:40.55,mushishishishishishi,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\blur1\4c&H41463D&\alpha&HFF&\t(0,3000,1.3,\alpha&H00&)\t(8760,0,0.7,\alpha&HFF&)\fscx130\fscy260\pos(192,164)}Mushi-Shi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:40.55,mushishishishishishi,,0,0,0,,{\shad10\bord1.2\blur0.6\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&H73756E&\alpha&HFF&\t(0,3000,1.3,\alpha&H00&)\t(8760,0,0.7,\alpha&HFF&)\fscx130\fscy260\pos(192,164)}Mushi-Shi
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.14,0:02:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that you're getting at?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.86,0:02:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the many strange symptoms {observed and }\Nnoted in mushi-shi records, this boy exhibits several{ of them}:
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.88,0:02:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,low body temperature,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.62,0:02:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,a delay in speech,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.65,0:03:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and, the rarest, webbing between the fingers.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.67,0:03:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about it?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.37,0:03:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're looking for trouble—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.61,0:03:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Presuming their cause to be mushi-related, \NI have medicine that can mitigate his symptoms.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.89,0:03:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely, you've noticed that these differences separate your son from other children.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.12,0:03:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It no doubt worries you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.33,0:03:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's swimming?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.63,0:03:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even in his sleep?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.57,0:04:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Your boy is afflicted with an Uko, or "Rain" mushi.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.58,0:04:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Separately, each Uko is too tiny to be seen by the naked eye.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.04,0:04:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But often, they mingle with the rain \Nand flow into rivers.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.68,0:04:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There, they come together \Nand form what resembles a big blue fish...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.41,0:04:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and flow into the sea to breed.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.11,0:04:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Their offspring mingle with water vapor {as it rises}from the sea
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.62,0:04:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and then fall as{like} rain on mountains and rivers.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.09,0:04:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They lead a rather simple existence.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.45,0:04:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But on occasion, an Uko may get left behind{ in a deep pool} while the others continue onward,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.97,0:04:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and to avoid being eaten{ by fish}, it may take up residence in a larger creature, such as a salamander.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.72,0:04:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And in extremely rare cases, \Neven a half-drowned human may become its host.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.39,0:05:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Although the person survives from nearly drowning,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.71,0:05:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,they often display symptoms like your son's,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.86,0:05:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and forcibly removing the Uko is impossible.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.42,0:05:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,One can only hope for a flash flood.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.09,0:05:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Uko sometimes leave their hosts{ on their own in an attempt} to try to ride \Nthe flood's turbulent waters and reach the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.60,0:05:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no telling when that might happen.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.24,0:05:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, first things first.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.92,0:05:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him this medicine, and watch over him.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.10,0:06:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.89,0:06:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.81,0:06:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times have I told you not to come here at night?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.40,0:06:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You had another dream about water, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.52,0:06:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.10,0:06:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.49,0:06:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My, you caught a big one today, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.77,0:07:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.40,0:07:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.43,0:07:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What do {\i1}you{\i0} want?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.60,0:07:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You should get lost.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.41,0:07:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that kid's body is as cold as a fish.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.67,0:07:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't be human.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.35,0:07:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Gross...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.79,0:07:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.37,0:07:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... That thing is huge!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.76,0:07:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots. Over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.82,0:07:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play together!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.76,0:07:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That way!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.04,0:07:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You suck!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.00,0:07:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.90,0:07:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, your body's not really all that cold.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.15,0:07:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.52,0:07:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you hear that from, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.95,0:07:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.23,0:08:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mommy?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.15,0:08:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.69,0:08:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does the river come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.25,0:08:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes from a valley deep in the mountains.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.29,0:08:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does that water{ in the mountain valley} come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.88,0:08:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes down from the clouds in the sky.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.09,0:08:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then where do the clouds in the sky come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.46,0:08:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.06,0:08:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. They're born from the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.28,0:08:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.86,0:08:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where this river goes.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.93,0:08:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a place with lots and lots of water.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.02,0:08:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.58,0:08:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How much is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.96,0:08:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.37,0:08:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've never seen it either...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.41,0:08:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've heard that there's water as far as the eye can see.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.58,0:08:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.68,0:08:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So the sea, the river, the rain, \Nand the clouds are all the same thing?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.57,0:08:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.02,0:08:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They may look different,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.72,0:09:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but they're actually all the same.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.11,0:09:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.28,0:09:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.27,0:09:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.60,0:09:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.60,0:09:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.49,0:09:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.65,0:09:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You look well.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.55,0:09:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're that old guy {from before }with the smoke.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.01,0:09:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Old"...{lmao}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.41,0:09:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it seems you're fine with the smoke now, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.02,0:09:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... I guess so.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.06,0:09:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears that the medicine is working.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.42,0:09:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.15,0:09:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,His body is much warmer now.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.14,0:09:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And before, he used to want nearly \Ntwo whole liters of water every day,{what, that's supposed to be a lot? doctors tell people to drink at least 3 litres a day...}{yeah, seriously. i probably go through more than that myself}{also, i looked this up in the manga because i was curious, and it's 一升 which is an old unit of measurement equating to 1.8 liters. what kind of world was this where drinking 1.8L of water in a day was strange...}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.43,0:10:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but now, he only wants about seven-tenths as much.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.69,0:10:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.51,0:10:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.93,0:10:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have more of the medicine you gave him?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.26,0:10:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I must caution you that this is about as much as you can ever hope from it.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.30,0:10:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, the mushi is still in him.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.35,0:10:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Uko do not typically choose humans as hosts,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.62,0:10:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,it's likely that its ties to him are not that deep.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.57,0:10:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,However, in the cases with salamanders,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.27,0:10:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,after only a few years, the hosts become one with the Uko and vanish into the waters.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.84,0:10:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,As you well know, this mushi is rather troublesome.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.74,0:10:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.90,0:10:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's going to be okay, isn't he?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.99,0:10:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.48,0:10:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be able to use the medicine to keep his symptoms at bay.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.09,0:10:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's enough for you,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.40,0:10:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I can come back again with more of the same medicine.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.77,0:10:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll give you a discount.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.02,0:11:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's enough for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.42,0:11:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man—
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.31,0:11:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me that.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.70,0:11:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When will you be back?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.23,0:11:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.73,0:11:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Early autumn, probably.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.37,0:11:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,See you then.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.56,0:11:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't drown anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.48,0:11:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But I never drowned.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.69,0:11:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.96,0:11:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have forgotten.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.56,0:11:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yuuta!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.85,0:11:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, see you later.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.41,0:11:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta? Hurry inside.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.83,0:11:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.25,0:12:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.53,0:12:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you thirsty?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.38,0:12:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't go to the river!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.75,0:12:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.53,0:12:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.06,0:12:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.22,0:12:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.68,0:12:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta, where are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.72,0:12:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginko!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.45,0:12:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard there's been a lot of rain here lately.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.97,0:12:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If it keeps raining, there may be a flash flood.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.60,0:12:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,While it's not without risk,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.33,0:12:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,if we succeed, we may be able to extract the Uko from him.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.23,0:12:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd like to try, I'll help you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.48,0:13:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.05,0:13:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be strong.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.19,0:13:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But... if we manage to do this,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.50,0:13:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll finally get to be like the other children,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.45,0:13:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and the other villagers will be able to accept you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.12,0:13:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stay still!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.40,0:13:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not safe.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.02,0:13:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.21,0:13:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go now.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.25,0:13:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.41,0:13:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.29,0:13:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.14,0:13:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to let you go!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.81,0:15:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.20,0:15:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.61,0:15:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.56,0:15:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta, please say something.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.82,0:15:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.41,0:15:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.63,0:15:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.33,0:15:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though the rain was so scary before,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.78,0:15:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not scary anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.97,0:15:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.85,0:15:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did the Uko leave?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.20,0:15:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mommy?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.34,0:15:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.03,0:15:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.30,0:16:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The river's all muddy now,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.38,0:16:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so let's go to the well near the mountains.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.03,0:16:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's still thirsty.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.17,0:16:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is the Uko still in him?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.45,0:16:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.25,0:16:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.63,0:16:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's burning up.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.16,0:16:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try to give him some water.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.49,0:16:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.89,0:16:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.74,0:17:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuu...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.97,0:17:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.18,0:17:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.75,0:17:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.04,0:17:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mommy?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.42,0:17:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does the river come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.38,0:17:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes from a valley deep in the mountains.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.13,0:17:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does that water{ in the mountain valley} come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.86,0:17:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes down from the clouds in the sky.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.65,0:17:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then where do the clouds in the sky come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.29,0:17:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They're born from the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.56,0:17:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.33,0:17:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where this river goes.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.34,0:18:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a place with lots and lots of water.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.45,0:18:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did he...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.67,0:18:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me earlier that he'd never drowned before.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.82,0:18:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you who drowned in the river, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.38,0:18:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.89,0:18:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened about ten months before he was born.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.12,0:18:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The current is strong today, for some reason.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.09,0:18:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it rained a lot up in the mountains...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.04,0:19:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When I came to, I was on the riverbank.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.34,0:19:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But my husband...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.22,0:19:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,His body was found at the bottom of the river.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.61,0:19:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Before long, I found out that I was with his child.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.96,0:19:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt so grateful that our child had been safe within me.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.16,0:19:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one more push!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.81,0:19:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep at it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.61,0:19:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost there!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.09,0:19:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.97,0:19:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.07,0:19:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When he was born, his body was ice-cold.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.90,0:19:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.28,0:20:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,he was still alive.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.98,0:20:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though everyone was afraid of him,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.55,0:20:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.61,0:20:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And even though he may not have been normal,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.01,0:20:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,he still managed to live this long.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.77,0:20:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So why? Why did this have to happen now?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.13,0:20:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Some say...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.57,0:20:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,an unborn child, floating within its mother's womb, \Nis closer to a creature of water than to a human.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.09,0:20:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, that may have been why your son became the Uko's host.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.41,0:20:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, as he continued growing within your womb,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.54,0:20:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,they became so intertwined \Nthat they became inseparable.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.27,0:20:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... This is all my fault, \Nfor becoming possessed by such a creature.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.65,0:21:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The day you almost drowned,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.36,0:21:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the only reason your son survived was that the Uko happened to save you.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.25,0:21:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, both of you would have died.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.09,0:21:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But he lived.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.54,0:21:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here, by your side...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.68,0:21:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,he lived.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.32,0:21:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So the sea, the river, the rain, \Nand the clouds are all the same thing?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.35,0:21:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.41,0:21:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They may look different,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.35,0:21:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but they're all actually the same.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.67,0:21:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta, where are you now?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you in the river?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.22,0:21:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.37,0:21:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.83,0:22:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?{These lead with ellipses because they come from an earlier part of the episode.}{i just really don't like how it looks, sorry}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.38,0:22:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not scary anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.06,0:22:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.91,0:22:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're everywhere.
